---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import servicesImg from '@/assets/home/services.png'
---

<style>
	@reference "../../../styles/global.css";

	.services-section {
		@apply bg-teal;
		@apply min-h-[735px];

		.services-image {
			@apply absolute;
			@apply top-[-50px] left-[-20px];
			@apply w-[318px];
		}

		.services-list {
			@apply mt-40;
			@apply flex flex-wrap gap-8;
			@apply mx-auto max-w-[784px];
		}

		.service-item {
			@apply bg-primary-light text-white;
			@apply w-[240px];
			@apply rounded-bl-[50px] px-8 py-6;
		}

		.service-item-title {
			@apply mb-4;
			@apply text-[16px] font-bold;
		}

		.service-item-text {
			@apply text-sm;
		}

		.btn-read-more {
			@apply mx-auto mt-10;
			@apply flex text-center;
			@apply max-w-[420px] rounded-full;
			@apply text-primary-light border-primary-light;
		}
	}
</style>

<section class="services-section py-20">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="flex gap-10">
			<div class="relative w-1/4 text-white">
				<Image src={servicesImg} alt="Hero Image" class="services-image" />
			</div>
			<div class="w-3/4 text-white">
				<h2>Services</h2>
				<h3 class="my-8 text-[28px]">mission-driven nearshoring for high-impact projects.</h3>
				<p>
					At Jaya, software is more than lines of code, it's a strategic asset built with intention,
					precision, and purpose. Our conscious software engineering model blends technical
					excellence with human understanding, enabling teams to collaborate better, ship faster,
					and deliver real business outcomes. With a nearshore structure, we work in sync with your
					operations, bridging cultural and timezone gaps to create long-term value from day one.
				</p>

				<p class="mt-5">
					Our remote-native model ensures timezone-aligned delivery, seamless collaboration, and
					long-term value wherever your team is based.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="services-list">
			<div class="service-item">
				<h3 class="service-item-title">nearshore staff augmentation</h3>
				<p class="service-item-text">
					With our nearshore consulting model, we connect the best technology professionals to
					companies seeking expertise to accelerate projects and strengthen their teams. We
					guarantee qualified talents with English fluency and low turnover, providing greater
					stability and efficiency for the market.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="service-item">
				<h3 class="service-item-title">outsourcing</h3>
				<p class="service-item-text">
					We offer flexible outsourcing models and manage specialized squads to support strategic
					projects and product delivery. Our approach ensures fast, aligned results, and extends to
					training programs and pro bono initiatives designed to multiply positive impact through
					technology.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="service-item">
